      "role": "user",
      "content": "the house is just so quiet now. it's like the air itself is empty. i wake up and for a second i forget, and then it hits me all over again that he's actually gone. i dont even know why i bother getting out of bed or making coffee or doing any of this. everything just feels so hollow.",
