    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like i'm going through the motions of a life that isn't mine anymore. like i'm just a ghost walking through rooms where he used to be. people say time heals or whatever, but it doesn't feel like that. it just feels like i'm being forced to endure something that shouldn't even be happening. it's so exhausting to keep existing in a world where he doesn't exist.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
